    {
      "name": "4. Orders",
      "description": "Orders link a User to a list of Products (Many-to-Many via join table 'order_products'). Create users and products before creating orders.\n\nThe request body sends IDs only (userId, productIds[]) — the service layer resolves them to entities.",
